  • Constructor Details

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(int appointmentId, String title, String description, String location, String type, Timestamp start, Timestamp end, Timestamp createDate, String createdBy, Timestamp lastUpdate, String lastUpdatedBy, int customerId, int userId, int contactId, Timestamp localStart, Timestamp localEnd)
      Constructor for Appointment Object. Called from SQL_queries for every row received from appointments table in database.
      Parameters:
      appointmentId - ID of Appointment.
      title - Title of Appointment.
      description - Description of Appointment.
      location - Location of Appointment.
      type - Type of Appointment
      start - Start time of Appointment in UTC Time.
      end - End time of Appointment in UTC Time.
      createDate - Date Appointment was created.
      createdBy - User that created Appointment.
      lastUpdate - Date Appointment was last updated.
      lastUpdatedBy - User that last Updated Appointment.
      customerId - Customer ID of Appointment.
      userId - User ID of Appointment.
      contactId - Contact ID of Appointment.
      localStart - Start time of Appointment in local time set on computer.
      localEnd - End Time of Appointment in local time set on computer.
